                    ".for host mode in SRC TRANSP SRC TUNNEL      IPS TRANSP IPS TUNNEL4 IPS TUNNEL6      ECO TUNNEL4 ECO TUNNEL6",
                    ".for ipv in IPV4 IPV6",
